thread.title: david huffine
thread.title_full: Carousel Checks reviewed by david huffine

author: david huffine
title: david huffine
text: Ordering was easy, shipment was standard. Checks were just as I ordered. Haven't had a chance to use any yet. The only minor complaint is that there were way more checks than I anticipated. I'm not sure if the web site said how many checks were in each set, but it's more than I will need in a lifetime. Accepting the terms and conditions as below just to review my order is ridiculous. Goes on forever, so if it says anything weird I don't accept.
